\ \ \ \ These\ flags\ are\ ignored.

O_NOCTTY
\ \ \ \ Not\ supported.

O_PATH
\ \ \ \ This\ flag\ will\ behave\ the\ same\ as\ is\ documented\ in\ the\ open(2)
\ \ \ \ man\-page.\ However,\ the\ use\ of\ the\ file\ descriptor\ returned\ as\ a
